/* Subsidence */  I removed the last two sentences, all of it was conjecture not based on fact and completely unsupported. If subsidence was occurring at the rates suggested here by the author, there would be massive structural instability and failures all throughout the greater Houston area, which simply don't occur. I would recommend removing this entire paragraph on subsidence, since when reviewing all of the references, the statements here are pretty much based on theory only
